  "title": "今日开源（2025-10-27）：PRIME-RL 开源突破，多阶段 RL 与协同进化系统加持，实现 IPhO 金牌级物理推理能力",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500023&idx=1&sn=27c83d1c6c9c78d261617fcdd79f3591",
  "date": "2025-10-27 10:16:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>每日发现最新LLM</span> <span>2025-10-27 18:16</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">中国香港</span></p>\n  <p>开源模型系列P1，以相机为中心的框架Puffin，强化学习框架DisCO，推理加速框架Fast-dLLM，算法CE-GPPO，深度研究AgentPokeeResearchOSS</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e6a04f7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8LxnJme4QS5NicssDuQA4cG4d5aicMxn2x2ssffnJVLylQS6Npuprakby9zRBuPMyShXIougkaUlw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100010333\" data-ratio=\"0.0859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 389px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17b00053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwuWicsSRFbFewfePZ1EiaVdtFvrJflfNa3P11kpGn8dhrOaAmmKQ3INqCXFZr2IrrUmmtkia9otecsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：P1</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"658\" data-imgfileid=\"100016362\" data-ratio=\"0.5666666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3c0febe6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8LxnJme4QS5NicssDuQA4cujg76uss9auOvmqelAia6sybLKaZT9LbVpqfVeLXpFibJCyicmkiaYdC9Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★P1项目是</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">PRIME-RL的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">首个开源模型系列，旨在通过多阶段强化学习和协同进化多智能体系统（PhysicsMinions）解决奥赛级别的物理推理问题。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目在2025年国际物理奥林匹克竞赛（IPhO）中达到了金牌水平。P1项目发布了两个模型版本：P1-30B-A3B和P1-235B-A22B，分别为30B和235B参数模型，展示了卓越的效率和性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/p1\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/p1</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Puffin</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"532\" data-imgfileid=\"100016361\" data-ratio=\"0.45555555555555555\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=734aa2cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8LxnJme4QS5NicssDuQA4cOq7dA5CCgSPzwFmlRNO2tvZD7UlmgUIEz8bHA6WmyZ0x7UDvdSt9ug%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Puffin项目首次尝试将相机几何无缝集成到一个统一的多模态模型中，提出了一个以相机为中心的框架，以推进多模态空间智能的发展。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了多种模型变体，以满足不同的应用需求，包括基础模型、增强空间推理和生成的模型，以及通过指令调优优化的模型，支持跨视图任务和复杂的多模态交互。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/puffin\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/puffin</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：DisCO</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"448\" data-imgfileid=\"100016359\" data-ratio=\"0.3851851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=87e6f66e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8LxnJme4QS5NicssDuQA4c7gs6HGbBkmx1DYibHHr2LwThWMicTft5JQgvY51ibyDgC7A2KibYpwGqaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DisCO是一种新的强化学习框架，基于判别学习方法。它通过提高正面答案的分数并降低负面答案的分数来训练模型，从而实现更快的收敛和更稳定的优化。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">DisCO旨在解决现有方法如GRPO在处理大规模推理模型时的难度偏差和熵崩溃等问题。通过使用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">非剪辑评分函数</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">简单的约束优化</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，DisCO在多个数学推理基准上表现优于GRPO及其变体。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/disco-optimization-ai\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/disco-optimization-ai</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Fast-dLLM</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"402\" data-imgfileid=\"100016360\" data-ratio=\"0.34444444444444444\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ad3b8785&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8LxnJme4QS5NicssDuQA4c7v7lHiaaic3GdlpYYr0kj33lTbyDibEGvTy5RYC8YErvHdRUvg0a3pObw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Fast-dLLM是一个基于扩散的大语言模型（LLM）推理加速框架，旨在为Dream和LLaDA等模型提供高效的推理支持。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">引入KV缓存</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">并行解码</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">等技术，显著减少了推理时间，同时保持了模型的准确性。Fast-dLLM的设计使其能够在不进行额外训练的情况下加速推理过程，适用于需要快速响应的大规模语言模型应用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fast-dllm\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fast-dllm</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：CE-GPPO</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"462\" data-imgfileid=\"100016358\" data-ratio=\"0.3962962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c62c04ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8LxnJme4QS5NicssDuQA4cuUwmt9w5EDuEU25ZdKvswGLoBwq99vLRWicKq7Lhoc2ZXjl5vZqBG0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★CE-GPPO是一种新颖的算法，通过在原生PPO中重新引入被剪裁的token的梯度，以温和且有界的方式实现。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过控制剪裁区间外token的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">梯度幅度</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，CE-GPPO能够实现探索与利用的平衡。理论和实验证明，CE-GPPO有效缓解了熵不稳定性。在数学推理基准测试中，CE-GPPO在不同模型规模上持续优于强基线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ce-gppo\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ce-gppo</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：PokeeResearchOSS</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"398\" data-imgfileid=\"100016363\" data-ratio=\"0.3416666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d64fd098&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8LxnJme4QS5NicssDuQA4cvyRT9pNJe3tXxmLlYQ6Dzpr1WiaibGrWxVul2NtBEPV3nV0x8vxIUaAw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★PokeeResearch-7B Agent 是一个先进的深度研究Agent，利用网络搜索和内容阅读能力，回答复杂问题。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目集成了最新的在线信息，提供全面的、引用丰富的研究报告。其架构基于高效的7B参数模型，能够在复杂推理任务中实现卓越的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;